title: Ghost Bat drones to be built in Australia to boost defence force's arsenal
description: Ghost Bat drones, the first military combat aircraft to be designed, engineered and manufactured in Australia for more than 50 years, are going from prototype to production to boost our defence force arsenal. #ghostbat #drone #military #defence #missile

title: Gang storms school with knives and axe | 7NEWS
description: Six teenagers have been charged over a stabbing attack at Ellenbrook Secondary College, where a gang armed with knives and an axe stormed the school targeting a 15-year-old student. The attack was allegedly motivated by revenge over online abuse, with a south-side gang travelling north of the river to carry out the assault. The victim was hospitalised with wounds to his arm and head, while two of the accused teens remain in custody and the youngest offender is just 13 years old.
